headline: TE Connectivity declares quarterly dividend
summary: TE Connectivity plc (NYSE: TEL) announced today that its board of directors declared a regular quarterly cash dividend of $0.71 per ordinary share, payable on December 12, 2025, to shareholders of record at the close of business on November 21, 2025.
